{"tid":2419610,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾國衞心繫「主席」 不斷以「主席」稱呼港澳辦主任夏寶龍","createTime":"2021-02-23T11:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T05:02:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":84,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"f9e336fc7fa94e495cdedee413565052fc448865","tid":2419610,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/olodWdN5Q931WOONm10xkwrUDjI=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LB6M2W3ASRD5PLRDN7BK6QYOLI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FolodWdN5Q931WOONm10xkwrUDjI%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLB6M2W3ASRD5PLRDN7BK6QYOLI.jpg&h=95f1bb24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年11月特首林鄭月娥喺立法會宣讀《施政報告》期間，因為喺立法會倒頭大睡「紅爆」、事後解釋服用咗令人眼瞓藥物嘅政制及內地事務局局長曾國衞，今日（23日）喺政總交代有關公職人員嘅參選宣誓修例安排時，又有「杰作」，竟然唔記得將電話校至靜音，電話響後仲攞起㩒咗幾下先放低，席間亦經常「雲遊」，唔記得記者提問，要由身邊嘅政制局常秘鄧忍光提水。<br />\n<br />\n辦公室擺咗中共國家主席習近平肖像瓷碟嘅曾國衞，心繫「主席」，就連港澳辦主任夏寶龍嘅職位都講錯，記者會上不斷以「主席」稱呼對方。<br />\n<br />\n由「武官」轉為「文官」嘅曾國衞一直被指唔熟書，除咗接受個別友好親建制傳媒專訪，上任至今極少接受傳媒公開訪問，今日面對記者連串追問都「現形」。<br />\n<br />\n當被問到政府嚟緊會由邊啲人為立法會議員同區議員宣誓時，曾國衞搵完一輪文件後，只講得出該局建議由民政事務局局長為區議員監誓，突然hang機咁要吩咐身邊嘅鄧忍光補充，補充政府建議由政務司司長張建宗代表特首為立法會議員監誓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210223/VU7XBYE75FGONNMQPFW3L5ARCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210223%2FVU7XBYE75FGONNMQPFW3L5ARCQ%2F&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv3%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=d5d8bd25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210223%2FVU7XBYE75FGONNMQPFW3L5ARCQ%2F&h=52e8e650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210223/VU7XBYE75FGONNMQPFW3L5ARCQ/</a>"},{"pid":"0b8946fde67d568a347f3e0620d550135f535e4a","tid":2419610,"uid":82640,"like":145,"dislike":1,"score":144,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:36:58.000Z","msg":"條友學歷（反映智力）根本應付唔到局長一職"},{"pid":"2378914927d5cbed7a04c30d4d972a504efd1145","tid":2419610,"uid":290404,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:37:40.000Z","msg":"證明佢真係共產黨員"},{"pid":"2514e48247815e861ba690a571423e1703278ae9","tid":2419610,"uid":144885,"like":84,"dislike":1,"score":83,"quote":{"pid":"0b8946fde67d568a347f3e0620d550135f535e4a","tid":2419610,"uid":82640,"like":145,"dislike":1,"score":144,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:36:58.000Z","msg":"條友學歷（反映智力）根本應付唔到局長一職"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"呢啲位不嬲都係弱智先請㗎啦<br />\n你睇劉江華就知"},{"pid":"83d5d4ec307f4eb0dcf8e5c5f149da0181f49c10","tid":2419610,"uid":53062,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:40:23.000Z","msg":"佢想夏主任坐習主席個位姐，中國官場習慣稱謂叫高一級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c51338092e9fc86cae1d5af8133603ef355862d","tid":2419610,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:41:14.000Z","msg":"想上位"},{"pid":"38c4fb99d165550aaa94573a70d6f11b5607b84c","tid":2419610,"uid":8014,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:42:06.000Z","msg":"2021: 識奶好過識人同識字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ffc2972483a553aa9b665418b53be709b76e6b","tid":2419610,"uid":63543,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"0b8946fde67d568a347f3e0620d550135f535e4a","tid":2419610,"uid":82640,"like":145,"dislike":1,"score":144,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:36:58.000Z","msg":"條友學歷（反映智力）根本應付唔到局長一職"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:42:08.000Z","msg":"佢暗示緊夏主席將會取代雜主席就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a80e4f108d4aee946a6569200edb8cc8b3bd20","tid":2419610,"uid":82640,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"2514e48247815e861ba690a571423e1703278ae9","tid":2419610,"uid":144885,"like":84,"dislike":1,"